# No Shared Theme Edits

Rule to prevent any modifications to shared theme files.

<rule>
name: no-shared-theme-edits
description: Prevent any modifications to files in shared-theme directories
filters:
  - type: file_path
    pattern: ".*/shared-theme/.*"
actions:
  - type: reject
    message: "Editing shared theme files is not allowed. These files should be treated as immutable."
examples:
  - input: "src/shared-theme/AppTheme.tsx"
    output: "Rejected: Cannot modify shared theme files"
metadata:
  priority: high
  version: 1.0
</rule>